## Project skills (`.cursor/skills/`)

| Skill | Use for |
|-------|---------|
| `save-hex-inspect` | Shell-side inspection of `.sav` bytes with `xxd`/`hexdump`/`od`/`dd`/`strings`/`python3` — locating offsets, FString decoding, desync hunting, save diffs |

## Harness

`pnpm re` runs `re.ts` (root) — drives the real parser against `public/SBS00.sav`, keeps every step + byte-read in memory, prints log tail + hex window on failure. Primary feedback loop while extending the parser.
